node.text:
To celebrate the first anniversary of Horizon Zero Dawn: The Frozen Wilds we sat down with Ashly Burch and talked about how she prepared for the role, her favorite scene and what it is like to see how people respond to Aloy.

#HorizonZeroDawn #PlayStation #PlayStation4 #Videogames #AshlyBurch

node.title: Ashly Burch explains what it was like to play Aloy in Horizon Zero Dawn.
